name: Hive'Zora Scout Report

Hive'Zora Scout ReportLevel 60

Contact Cenarion Scout Azenel inside Hive'Zora and return the Hive'Zora Scout Report to Windcaller Proudhorn at Cenarion Hold.  You must also bring Tactical Task Briefing VI in order to complete this quest.

Requirements:
- Hive'Zora Scout Report
